00:13:00,333 --> 00:13:01,333
within stable levels.

245
00:13:01,416 --> 00:13:02,583
[OPERATOR 1D]
Internal quantum coils

246
00:13:02,666 --> 00:13:04,041
at optimum capacity.

247
00:13:04,125 --> 00:13:06,416
Crafts are fully tuned
and ready to go.

248
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,791
Vectors, launch!

249
00:13:11,458 --> 00:13:16,083
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi. Koi. Koi. Koi. Koi.

250
00:13:18,208 --> 00:13:21,458
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi!

251
00:13:27,041 --> 00:13:29,750
Okey doke, Hayato. Let's
give this thing the biz!

252
00:13:29,833 --> 00:13:33,833
On my mark. Verbalize Merge!

253
00:13:33,916 --> 00:13:37,625
[HAYATO, TSUTOMU]
Dash... Aquarion!

254
00:13:46,125 --> 00:13:47,208
[HAYATO, TSUTOMU]
Jin!

255
00:13:48,291 --> 00:13:50,791
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi, Koi, Koi, Koi!

256
00:13:50,875 --> 00:13:51,666
[MAIA]
You're late.

257
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:53,375
[KOKONE]
I-I'm sorry!

258
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:55,833
[SHOKO] By these readings,
word concept corrosion

259
00:13:55,916 --> 00:13:57,958
rate is at 42% and rising.

260
00:13:58,041 --> 00:13:59,416
Very well then, boys.

261
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:01,125
You heard the stats:
what I need you to do

262
00:14:01,208 --> 00:14:03,083
for now is focus
on stall tactics.

263
00:14:03,166 --> 00:14:04,458
[gasps]

264
00:14:05,583 --> 00:14:09,583
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi!

265
00:14:09,666 --> 00:14:11,291
Koi!

266
00:14:14,458 --> 00:14:15,500
[TSUTOMU]
Savior Man doesn't get

267
00:14:15,583 --> 00:14:19,083
to strut his stuff
on this one! Ha, ha!

268
00:14:19,166 --> 00:14:21,708
[SAKURAKO] Weapons are an
effective mitigating strategy.

269
00:14:21,791 --> 00:14:24,500
But they're not powerful enough
to finish off the M.J.B.K.

270
00:14:24,583 --> 00:14:25,833
They know the score.

271
00:14:25,916 --> 00:14:28,875
They'll switch to Verbalism
once it's weakened.

272
00:14:28,958 --> 00:14:30,083
No, I...

273
00:14:30,166 --> 00:14:32,750
I have to... I have
to protect love!

274
00:14:39,625 --> 00:14:41,375
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi!

275
00:14:42,541 --> 00:14:44,958
[TSUTOMU]
Well, that was easy.

276
00:14:45,041 --> 00:14:45,708
[AKIRA]
Wait.

277
00:14:45,791 --> 00:14:46,833
[SAKURAKO gasps]

278
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:52,583
[SAKURAKO]
Kujyo, Domon! Be careful!

279
00:14:52,666 --> 00:14:54,208
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi.

280
00:14:54,291 --> 00:14:55,541
What the hell?

281
00:14:55,625 --> 00:14:58,708
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi. Koi.

282
00:14:58,791 --> 00:15:00,458
I thought you said
you loved me, creep!

283
00:15:00,541 --> 00:15:01,958
Oh, whatever!
Don't even go there!

284
00:15:02,041 --> 00:15:03,041
You said it first!

285
00:15:03,125 --> 00:15:04,083
[NEWHALF 4A]
Bastard!

286
00:15:04,166 --> 00:15:05,000
[NEWHALF 4B]
Get off of me!

287
00:15:05,083 --> 00:15:06,500
There is nothing between us!

288
00:15:06,583 --> 00:15:07,958
[NEWHALF 4A]
I hate you!

289
00:15:10,375 --> 00:15:12,250
[SHOKO] Word corrosion
rate still rising.

290
00:15:12,333 --> 00:15:14,291
Current reading is over 60%!

291
00:15:14,375 --> 00:15:16,166
[SAKURAKO] If it breaks down
in the Logos World,

292
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:17,416
we're in trouble.

293
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:19,166
The very concept it's
meant to represent will

294
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:21,458
completely vanish
from existence!

295
00:15:21,541 --> 00:15:22,708
We can't let that happen!

296
00:15:22,791 --> 00:15:23,958
[alarm beeps]

297
00:15:24,041 --> 00:15:26,875
[gasps] Another vector
is preparing to launch.

298
00:15:26,958 --> 00:15:28,500
I'll get a visual.

299
00:15:30,583 --> 00:15:33,291
[SAKURAKO]
Kikogami! What are you doing?

300
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:39,250
I have to save my love.
I'm sorry. I m-must.

301
00:15:40,125 --> 00:15:43,166
What's gotten into her?
She does this now?

302
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:44,583
Maia, let's get in there!

303
00:15:44,666 --> 00:15:45,625
Yeah.

304
00:15:46,833 --> 00:15:48,041
[KOKONE]
Verbalize!

305
00:15:50,416 --> 00:15:51,958
[HAYATO]
Tsutomu! Let's finish this!

306
00:15:52,041 --> 00:15:54,041
[TSUTOMU]
You don't gotta tell me twice!

307
00:16:00,541 --> 00:16:01,750
Wha--? Kokone?

308
00:16:01,833 --> 00:16:03,875
What is she doing? Kikogami!

309
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,875
[TSUTOMU, HAYATO
grunting, groaning]

310
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,416
[AKIRA]
Time to Merge.

311
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:13,791
[MAIA]
You think?

312
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:19,583
Verbalize Merge. Now shout.

313
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:22,833
[BOTH]
Aquarion!

314
00:16:31,541 --> 00:16:33,083
Akira.

315
00:16:36,708 --> 00:16:37,708
[MAIA]
Kikogami!

316
00:16:37,791 --> 00:16:40,750
Akira, I... I
w-wanted to tell you.

317
00:16:42,083 --> 00:16:43,916
[MAIA grunts]
What the--?

318
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:44,916
What's happening?

319
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,791
Did they Merge or didn't they?

320
00:16:47,875 --> 00:16:50,750
[MAIA] I don't understand.
Is the formation off?

321
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:53,166
[AKIRA]
Not just off. Evil.

322
00:16:54,541 --> 00:16:56,333
[AKIRA]
Aku-arion.

323
00:16:57,875 --> 00:16:59,708
[MAIA]
What?

324
00:16:59,791 --> 00:17:00,916
[AKIRA, MAIA yelp]

325
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:04,291
[TSUTOMU] Yeah, so, um,
that didn't go well.

326
00:17:04,375 --> 00:17:05,500
What was that for?

327
00:17:05,583 --> 00:17:07,833
[MAIA] The controls have
a mind of their own!

328
00:17:10,416 --> 00:17:11,583
[AKIRA groans]

329
00:17:11,666 --> 00:17:14,250
[KOKONE panting]

330
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:16,500
[KOKONE]
It's, it's so hot.

331
00:17:16,583 --> 00:17:19,500
I can't hold back...
my feelings!

332
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:20,583
Hang in there!

333
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:23,000
Try not to lose
your head! Stay sane!

334
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:25,708
But... But I... I c-can't!

335
00:17:25,791 --> 00:17:27,541
[SAKURAKO]
Don't suppress the Verbalism!

336
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:29,708
It's playing havoc
with your voice!

337
00:17:29,791 --> 00:17:32,666
Keep trying to hold back,
and you'll kill it entirely!

338
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:34,666
Speak from the heart, damn it!

339
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:37,083
Now! You have to give
your feelings voice!

340
00:17:37,166 --> 00:17:39,083
[KOKONE]
I... I-I can't!

341
00:17:39,166 --> 00:17:40,458
Why on earth not?

342
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:41,875
[KOKONE]
Because!

343
00:17:44,291 --> 00:17:46,333
Miss Kokone? I love you!

344
00:17:46,416 --> 00:17:48,375
Will you be my wife someday?

345
00:17:48,458 --> 00:17:50,208
You should come
and live with me!

346
00:17:50,291 --> 00:17:51,708
Oh, guys.

347
00:17:51,791 --> 00:17:54,791
I'm sorry, but I'm just not
that into you. See ya later!

348
00:17:56,583 --> 00:17:59,708
[KOKONE]
See ya later...

349
00:17:59,791 --> 00:18:01,791
[LITTLE BOYS whine]

350
00:18:06,333 --> 00:18:07,958
[LITTLE BOY 4A giggles]

351
00:18:13,166 --> 00:18:16,125
[KOKONE]
See ya later...

352
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:23,250
[LITTLE BOY 4A'S MOM sobbing]

353
00:18:23,333 --> 00:18:24,625
[LITTLE BOY 4C]
This is all your fault!

354
00:18:24,708 --> 00:18:28,166
If you weren't so mean
to him, he'd still be alive!

355
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:31,583
[KOKONE whimpers]

356
00:18:31,666 --> 00:18:36,500
[KOKONE sobs]

357
00:18:36,583 --> 00:18:39,166
[DOCTOR 4A] You say she's
having issues with speaking?

358
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:40,500
Oh, dear.

359
00:18:40,583 --> 00:18:42,250
I... I...

360
00:18:42,333 --> 00:18:45,208
...try but, then I c-can't.

361
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:48,250
It's more than likely
brought on by stress.

362
00:18:48,333 --> 00:18:52,208
The treatments will
take some time.

363
00:18:52,291 --> 00:18:57,833
[KOKONE] I... I-I can't.
When I say how I feel...

364
00:18:57,916 --> 00:19:00,041
...bad things happen!

365
00:19:00,125 --> 00:19:02,416
[AKIRA] You're afraid of
hurting someone again.

366
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,750
[gasps]

367
00:19:03,833 --> 00:19:06,250
[AKIRA] Aquarion showed me
what you went through.

368
00:19:06,333 --> 00:19:09,083
I understand. You've
learned the hard way

369
00:19:09,166 --> 00:19:12,333
just how powerful
the voice can be.

370
00:19:12,416 --> 00:19:14,541
You've come to fear that power.

371
00:19:14,625 --> 00:19:16,375
You're convinced that
every time you use it,

372
00:19:16,458 --> 00:19:18,541
someone pays the price.

373
00:19:20,250 --> 00:19:21,958
Come on! Somebody do something!

374
00:19:22,041 --> 00:19:23,708
Calm down. Let the man talk!

375
00:19:23,791 --> 00:19:26,750
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Heartbreak!

376
00:19:31,041 --> 00:19:34,416
[AKIRA] Thing is,
you've got it backwards.

377
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:36,666
Your voice gives me strength.

378
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:40,625
Whatever's behind it,
I can deal. I promise.

379
00:19:42,083 --> 00:19:43,333
You really mean it?

380
00:19:43,416 --> 00:19:46,458
[AKIRA] Damn right, I do!
Give me all you got!

381
00:19:46,541 --> 00:19:48,750
Let your voice be heard!

382
00:19:51,041 --> 00:19:52,541
[KOKONE]
Akira and Maia.

383
00:19:52,625 --> 00:19:55,000
I'm so jealous of that bond.

384
00:19:55,083 --> 00:19:59,375
They're in Gattai together,
but, I don't care.

385
00:20:00,583 --> 00:20:02,250
I want to be part!

386
00:20:02,333 --> 00:20:05,666
I want to Gattai
with both of you!

387
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:09,458
[AKIRA] A threesome it is,
then. Let's do this!

388
00:20:09,541 --> 00:20:11,166
Go, Genesis Merge!

389
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,458
Like a star!

390
00:20:12,541 --> 00:20:16,958
[KOKONE, MAIA, AKIRA]
Shine on, Aquarion!

391
00:20:24,541 --> 00:20:26,625
[MAIA]
Oh, my. This is...

392
00:20:26,708 --> 00:20:28,000
[KOKONE]
Wow.

393
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:30,416
I didn't think you could do
this with three people!

394
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:32,666
It feels amazing!

395
00:20:48,125 --> 00:20:50,666
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi! Koi! Koi! Koi! Koi!

396
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:55,291
[MAIA, KOKONE, AKIRA]
Angel!

397
00:20:55,375 --> 00:20:56,666
[SAKURAKO]
Fascinating!

398
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:59,333
A Merge Form we've
never seen before!

399
00:20:59,416 --> 00:21:01,083
Three hearts become as one,

400
00:21:01,166 --> 00:21:04,166
like the Legend of Orihime
and Hikoboshi and Susan!

401
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:05,541
How glorious!

402
00:21:05,625 --> 00:21:07,583
Hang on, who the heck is Susan?

403
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:09,125
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi!

404
00:21:09,208 --> 00:21:11,875
[SHOKO gasps] Word corrosion
rate is climbing rapidly, ma'am!

405
00:21:11,958 --> 00:21:14,666
We're just shy of the
critical threshold!

406
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:19,750
[KOKONE] Give my love a
voice. Let it fly free.

407
00:21:42,166 --> 00:21:43,666
[AKIRA]
Verbalize.

408
00:21:45,625 --> 00:21:47,166
[MAIA, AKIRA, KOKONE]
Moonlight Cannon!

409
00:21:47,250 --> 00:21:48,208
[M.J.B.K. 4A]
Koi!

410
00:21:48,291 --> 00:21:49,500
Heads up!

411
00:21:56,416 --> 00:21:57,708
Are you all right?

412
00:21:57,791 --> 00:22:00,333
Y-Yeah.

413
00:22:00,416 --> 00:22:03,083
Would you care to explain
why you left me alone?

414
00:22:03,166 --> 00:22:04,625
I knew you could hold your own.

415
00:22:04,708 --> 00:22:07,375
Ugh! You intolerable miscreant.

416
00:22:14,875 --> 00:22:18,166
[KOKONE] "'W-We will not
give in to greedy p-pigs,'

417
00:22:18,250 --> 00:22:20,625
s-said the noble swan.

418
00:22:20,708 --> 00:22:24,625
'Because we...
Because we have love!'"

419
00:22:29,291 --> 00:22:32,791
[SAKURAKO] Well. I'd say
that went swimmingly.

420
00:22:32,875 --> 00:22:34,291
Huh?

421
00:22:35,458 --> 00:22:36,875
[KOKONE]
What do I do?

422
00:22:36,958 --> 00:22:42,166
The M.J.B.K. is gone, but...
I still have these feelings.

423
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:43,666
[SUBETE]
If I'm seeing this correctly,

424
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:46,041
she was spotted
somewhere around here.

425
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:56,416
Father?

426
00:24:27,958 --> 00:24:30,416
Sunblock: check!
Change of panties: check!

427
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:32,708
Hey, Ka-Ka-Karan,
are you going on a trip?

428
00:24:32,791 --> 00:24:34,750
Remember: you're only
allowed two sweets per day.

429
00:24:34,833 --> 00:24:36,000
I know!

430
00:24:36,083 --> 00:24:37,583
[KOKONE] Sounds like a
p-picnic. Ha-Have fun!

431
00:24:37,666 --> 00:24:38,666
Make sure you
have your cellphone,

432
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:40,041
your compass, and your
safety goggles!

433
00:24:40,125 --> 00:24:41,083
I know!

434
00:24:41,166 --> 00:24:42,916
Wh-Wh-Where are you
planning to go?

435
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,333
Next: Episode Five!

436
00:24:44,416 --> 00:24:46,791
[SHOKO]
"Take it Back! Our Summer!"

